a.xlink:title: AddGyrationRadius adds gyration radius to an Element object.
AddMap adds a new property by mapping from an existing property.
Element is a Generator containing data element (or entity) as a Json object.
Trampoline class to bind Element class to Python.
Generator is an abstract class to generate data.
GenDict is a dictionary (or map) of Generator objects.
GenList is a list (or vector) of Generator objects.
Updater is an abstract class to update data held by an Element object.
Adder adds new properties (keys and values) to non-empty Element::data.
Filter removes items in array Element::data if the items fail user-defined criteria.
AddChildIDs adds id property of a child Element object to a parent Element object.
AddChildPositions adds relative positions of a child Element object to a parent Element object...
AddCoMPosition adds center of mass to an Element object as its unwrapped position.
AddInertiaMoment adds inertia moment to an Element object.
AddMolecularOrientation adds molecular orientation (order parameter) to an Element object...
AddWrappedPosition adds wrapped positions of an Element object.
FilSet applies filtering using sets of acceptable values.
